pageContext.claim: “We have great ideas having to do with Syria. And it's working out very well. We're knocking the hell out of ISIS, and we're bringing our folks back home. And we're going to always have a presence. And it's working out very well. A lot of things are working out well.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump made these comments as his Syria policy appeared in disarray, causing by the resignation of key officials to protest his decision to abruptly withdraw troops from Syria.
